      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Senator Henry Heitfeldt of Lew\niston. Idaho. was In the city this\nmorning on business connected with\nthe large irrigation proposition which\nprominent Idaho men have under\ntaken. Said Senator Heitfeldt:\n\n\nLewiston IL unusually prosperous\nthis season. Lots OF money in circu-\nlation and everyone 10 corresponding\nly well off. One thing quite noticeable\nis that soon lots of Lewiston people\nand others as well will be going into\nthe Buffalo Hump country, which\npromises TO turn out we'll this year.\n\n\nMany Of our people have bought\nstock and property In that district\nand express much satisfaction at\ntheir investment\""
    }
